Xikonajsi itech Mozilla Add-Ons


;How Lightbeam Works
Keniuj tekiti Lightbeam


;Download and run the Lightbeam add-on in your Firefox browser.
Xikontemoui uan xikontekitilti tamajsikayot Lightbeam itech monavegador Firefox.


;Lightbeam will create a record of events for every site you visit and every third party site that is stored locally on your browser.
Lightbeam kinijkuilos tachiualismej ika sejsemej sitios tein tikonkalpano uan sejsemej sitios ininaxkauan oksekin tein mochanchiuaj itech monavegador.


;Lightbeam visually graphs these events to highlight the interactions between sites you intentionally visit and the third parties.
Lightbeam kinnextia nejin tachiualismej kemej yeskiaj taixkopimej uan ijkon kinyeknextia kemej mouikaj sitos tein tikonkalpanojtinemi uan sitios teaxkauan.


;Lightbeam will continue to add to your graph as you browse the Web. You can stop Lightbeam at any time by disabling it or uninstalling the add-on. Your Lightbeam data can be easily saved or deleted.
Lightbeam kintalijtiyas taixkopimej gráficos ijkuak tikontatekiujtis Web. Komo tikonseuis oso tikonkixtis nejin tamajsikayot, tionuelis tikonchiua maj Lightbeam amo tekiti. Nochi tein kipia Lightbeam tein moaxka amo ouij tionuelis tikoneuas oso tikonpolos.


;Tracking & privacy
Tetoktilia uan teyekpia


;Not all tracking is bad. Many services rely on user data to provide relevant content and enhance your online experience.
Iksa kuali yetok maj tetoktiliaj. Sekin nepaleuilmej kikuij tein kiajsiskej ijkuak mitstoktiliskej uan ijkon tionuelis tikonyektalis kemej tikontatekiujtis Internet.


;But tracking can happen without the user’s knowledge.
Sayoj ke uelis tetoktiliskej uan tokniuj amo kimatis.


;That’s not okay for some.
Sekin kinemiliaj amo kuali yetok nejin.


;It should be you who decides when, how and if you want your browsing data to be shared. We recognize the importance of transparency and our mission is all about empowering users — both with tools and information.
Semi kuali maj tikonixtalis keman, keniuj uan komo tikonnekis tikinonnextilis oksekin tein tikonchiujtinemi Iternet. Tejuan tiktayekanaltia nochin uelis kiitaskej tein mochiujtok, uan totekiuj yejua tikkauiliskej tokniuan uelis kiixtaliskej tein kinekiskej —ika manamikmej uan taman tein tiktematiltiaj.


;We’re building this crowd-sourced directory to encourage users to visualize the state of tracking as an aggregate and to examine relationships that exist on the Web.
Tikchiujtokej nejin directorio ika miak naluayoliskayomej, tein kinolinis tokniuan kiyekitaskej keniuj kintoktiliskej, kemej yeskia se tamajsikayot, uan ijkon uelis kiitaskej keniuj mouikaj tein moajsij itech Web.


;Visualize your data
xikonita nochi tein tikonkaujtinemi tein moaxka.


;After you download and install the Lightbeam add-on to Firefox, it will begin to create a real time visualization of the websites you visit and all the third parties that are also active on those pages.
Satepan tikontemouij uan tikontalij Lightbeam ika Firefox motepos, peuas kichiuas tiempo tein yekmelauj taixkopimej nochi sitios web tein tikonkalpanos uan nochi sitios tein teaxkauan uan tein tekitij itech nejin páginas.


;Analyze your connections
Xikonyekita motanajnamiktilisuan.


;As your visualizations grow, you can take a closer look into the relationships between the various first and third party sites that are stored in your data. You can also reset or save your data at any time.
Kemej momiakiliaj tein tikonitstijtiuitse, okachi kuali tionuelis tikonitas keniuj mouikaj tayekantokej sitios uan sitios tein teaxkauan tein mochanchiuaj itech taman tein moaxkauan. Uan no tionuelis oksepa tikonpeualtis oso tikoneuas tein moaxka ijkuak tikonnekis.


;To help us, you can contribute your data to our Lightbeam database.
Xitechpaleuis uan xitechmaktili datos tein moaxkauan uan tiktaliliskej base tein datos tein poui Lightbeam.


;Supported by the Ford Foundation
Kipaleuia nechikol Ford Foundation


;The work at the Ford Foundation focuses on building outreach campaigns to help people understand online data tracking — both the benefits and the issues
Nechikol Ford Foundation kitematiltia keniuj uelis kiajsikamatiskej toni kiijtosneki tetoktiliaj itech Internet, uan nepaleuilis uan nepololmej tein nejin kininuika tokniuan.


