# About page
;About Lightbeam
Kampa se uelis okachi momachtis Lightbeam


;Lightbeam visualizes the relationships between the sites you visit and the third party sites that are active on those pages.
Lightbeam kinextia keniuj mouikaj sitios tein tikonkalpanoua iuan sitios tein teaxkauan tein tekititokej itech nejon páginas.


;How the add-on works
Keniuj tamasijkayot tekiti.


